            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: IRT 457: zwischen 266 und 267. Datierung: IRT 469: zwischen Herbst 352 und Ende 354. Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 469: 5.5-6 IRT 457 was carved over an erased previous inscription for an equestrian statue, later IRT 469 was carved on the left side. IRT 469 is carved on two columns.</p>
